│ vector operands. The core issue is that it sometimes uses a PHI node defined inside a loop when it should be using that PHI's incoming value from the loop's preheader.                  │
│                                                                                                                                                                                          │
│ My previous attempts have failed due to compilation errors, indicating I was calling non-existent functions or placing code in the wrong scope. The build environment has also shown     │
│ confusing behavior by reporting errors from old, discarded patches.                                                                                                                      │
